      "author": "thomasblc",
      "description": "Correctness + security hardening (from a triple-review) plus first onboarding improvements. No breaking changes.\n\n**Data integrity:** fixed a P0 where OCR'd images were dropped from the search index on every incremental run; \"Reindex (full)\" now drops deleted notes; OCR respects excluded folders.\n\n**Security:** `daemon.json`/token now `0600` and the config dir `0700` (the bearer token was world-readable); training path-traversal via `vaultId` closed; chat answers strip remote images (an exfil vector via a synced/shared note); constant-time token compare.\n\n**Stability:** reliable reconnect after a companion restart; the idle timer no longer interrupts a training run; chat/train worker-lock race fixed; Connect tab no longer stacks panels; over-size uploads no longer hang.\n\n**Onboarding & UX:** first-run Setup panel with a staged model download (embeddings first) + progress bar; chat model picker (0.6B/1.7B/4B/8B) with RAM guidance; streaming Markdown render + a Stop button.\n\nFull notes: see CHANGELOG.md. BRAT-installable (`thomasblc/obsidian-qvac`).",
