      "description": "First beta of QVAC for Obsidian. Local AI for your vault: chat with citations, semantic search, related-notes, inline writing commands, OCR, and an optional model fine-tuned on your own notes. Nothing leaves your machine.\n\n**Install via BRAT:** add `thomasblc/obsidian-qvac`. You also need the QVAC companion running (see the README). Desktop only, macOS first.\n\nAssets below are the three Obsidian plugin files (main.js, manifest.json, styles.css).",
